---
import FeatureCard from '@chassis-ui/docs/components/FeatureCard.astro'
---

<section class="home-section py-3xlarge medium:py-6xlarge">
  <div class="container 2xlarge section-content py-3xlarge medium:py-6xlarge">
    <div class="row mb-3xlarge medium:mb-6xlarge">
      <div class="section-header col large:col-10 xlarge:col-8 text-center mx-auto">
        <h2
          class="section-title font-3xlarge medium:font-4xlarge large:font-5xlarge mb-xsmall medium:mb-small large:mb-medium"
        >
          <span class="font-normal d-block">Built for Complex</span> Multi-Brand Organizations
        </h2>
        <p class="section-body medium:font-large large:font-xlarge m-0">
          A comprehensive token system for teams managing multiple brands, themes, and platforms
          from a single repository.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-features row row-cols-1 medium:row-cols-2 g-medium medium:g-xlarge">
      <div class="col">
        <FeatureCard icon="cx-rectangle-history">
          <Fragment slot="title">Git-Based Version Control</Fragment>
          <Fragment slot="body">
            Every token change tracked in Git with complete version history. Review token diffs in
            pull requests, rollback to any previous state, trace design decisions over time.
          </Fragment>
        </FeatureCard>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <FeatureCard icon="cx-rocket">
          <Fragment slot="title">Extensible Transform Pipeline</Fragment>
          <Fragment slot="body">
            Built on Style Dictionary's transform system. Add custom validators, formatters, and
            transforms to enforce your design standards or specific needs.
          </Fragment>
        </FeatureCard>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <FeatureCard icon="cx-brackets-curly">
          <Fragment slot="title">W3C DTCG Compliant</Fragment>
          <Fragment slot="body">
            Token format follows the W3C Design Tokens Community Group specification. Future-proof
            architecture ensures compatibility with emerging tools and standards.
          </Fragment>
        </FeatureCard>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <FeatureCard icon="cx-thumbs-up">
          <Fragment slot="title">Platform Agnostic</Fragment>
          <Fragment slot="body">
            Works with any JavaScript framework or no framework at all. Platform outputs support
            Swift Package Manager for iOS and Gradle for Android.
          </Fragment>
        </FeatureCard>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <FeatureCard icon="cx-refresh">
          <Fragment slot="title">Automated Workflows</Fragment>
          <Fragment slot="body">
            Eliminates manual token management, saving you time and effort, with support for
            seamless integration into CI/CD pipelines and version control.
          </Fragment>
        </FeatureCard>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <FeatureCard icon="cx-laptop-code">
          <Fragment slot="title">Developer-Friendly</Fragment>
          <Fragment slot="body">
            Easily import tokens as SCSS variables for web, Swift for iOS, and XML for Android
            development. Works seamlessly with any bundler you choose.
          </Fragment>
        </FeatureCard>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
